Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.22,0:00:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{=2}What a pleasant surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.16,0:00:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary Horu-
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.12,0:00:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.64,0:00:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd prefer Takanashi Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.90,0:00:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a change of plans, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.44,0:00:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to once again extend an offer to you, \N the wielder of the strongest Mystic in Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.62,0:00:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.66,0:00:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My, now, please, calm yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.54,0:00:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an offer that you could not \Npossibly refuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.94,0:00:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll find it worth your attention.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.74,0:02:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We will end today's segment with \Nfootage from the Abydos district.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.20,0:02:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that despite the recent explosion, \Nthe desert remains the same as ever.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.14,0:02:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today's news.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.50,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this happen to me...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.06,0:03:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, President Hina, how many \Nmore of these should I write?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.66,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done about two hundred now, haven't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.82,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say yourself that \Nyou would write a thousand?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.56,0:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, what I meant was I was\N so ashamed that I {\i1}could{\i0} write a thousand.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Less talking, more writing.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.44,0:03:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, had you met that \NAbydos student Hoshino before?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I had done research on her \Nwhile I was in the intelligence division.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But this was my first time meeting her myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke as if you knew her well, \N so I assumed you had met before.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A true elite, a genius by all standards.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.00,0:04:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The intelligence division's analysis two years ago \Nlisted her as a latent threat to Gehenna.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She certainly didn't give me that impression.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.24,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako. You shouldn't judge people based on appearance.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that she seemed like \Nan entirely different person.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.42,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She used to be highly aggressive, \N specialized in offensive tactics.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.94,0:04:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She struck me as a rough, \Nyet dangerously sharp individual.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, putting that aside for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.20,0:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had gone on and engaged then, \Nwe would have lost over half of our forces.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All because you jumped the gun, Ako.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.70,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I had analysed their combat capability, \N but there was nothing like that in the report.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.84,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she did just disappear off the grid one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.70,0:04:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The intelligence division may have stopped \Nconsidering her a threat at some point.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.14,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to know more, \N you should try digging through the old files.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako, I don't see you writing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.72,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've remained in Abydos\N all this time without leaving.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.64,0:05:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, where should I put this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.38,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, the crime against calligraphy \Nthat Aru poured all her talents into making.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.78,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just chuck it in the bin.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.50,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.50,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something she made \Nfor calligraphy class, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess she might say \N she wants to bring it along.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Aru...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She obviously really doesn't want to move.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.76,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I get how she feels, but the Prefects\N will be all over this place.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And since we failed, the client's \Ngonna be gunning for us too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.02,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.78,0:05:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, our little Abydos problem \Nended up going unsolved after all, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,W-we didn't have a choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.14,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't just turn around and attack \Nthe same people who fought alongside us!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.60,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Outlaws have to know when to let go of the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So chin up and say goodbye to this old place.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kayoko, what do we do with this?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we really need that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have smartphones, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about convenience, \Nit's about the feel!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.14,0:06:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.36,0:06:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This retro design is perfect for an \Noutlaw's office, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I think so, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cool, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd understand, Haruka!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a retreat. It's our next step forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.76,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how bad things may be now, \Nwe'll be back in this office one day. Just you wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.52,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because we're real, bonafide outlaws!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we finally say goodbye to this place.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.26,0:07:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't even pay last month's rent, \Nso we apparently need to leave today.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Aru.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we're camping tonight!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.00,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,, W-w-w-what do you mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be everything loaded.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Aru.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've camped out plenty of times by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just going back to how things were before.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Going back...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're not going back!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We are moving forward!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, where to?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not like we have anywhere {\i1}to{\i0} go.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go back to Gehenna?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.28,0:08:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you're Sunaookami Shiroko, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.78,0:08:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{nn}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not here for a rematch, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.38,0:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was biking in the area, \Nand I happened to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.62,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.80,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... about the other day...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for helping us!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,, And also, about the ramen shop...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgiven you for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do seem like you're sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe us one. How's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you were the ones \Nwho left that bag, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I have no idea what you mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about a bag filled with money!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I've never even heard of such a thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.48,0:09:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru, you know you've basically admitted to it \Nby mentioning the money.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.82,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you stole that money \Nwhen you robbed the bank, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't stooped far enough \Nto keep it just because we found it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Outlaws have standards too!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well look who's sassy now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.52,0:09:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I went ahead and delivered the bag to the boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.62,0:09:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever we hear the voices of clients\N crying out for Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru, we should get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find a place to camp for tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.04,0:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no intention of acting like \Nwe're suddenly best friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm- \NAn outlaw, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I see you again?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.62,0:10:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that ramen shop ever opens again, \Nmaybe we'll meet there again someday?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time for us to venture out ourselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Out where? \NInto the sunset!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still the middle of the day.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the details. Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to visit you, boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.40,0:10:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, don't worry 'bout me. \N'Tis but a scratch.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.18,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, that was quite the blast. \NI'm sure glad nobody was hurt besides me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.34,0:11:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiba Seki Ramen, your store...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.40,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry you lost \Nyour part-time job, Serika.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about that, boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.56,0:11:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about closing my shop for good anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.00,0:11:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happened sooner than I expected is all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the shop?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.46,0:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'see, I had received an eviction notice a while back.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.02,0:11:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An eviction notice? That shouldn't be possible!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.84,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ownership of the buildings within the \NAbydos district belong to the school.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.42,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so you girls didn't know, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.90,0:11:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A few years ago, the buildings and the land \Nstopped belonging to the student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.10,0:11:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're within the Abydos district.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika, did you know about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is the first I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean there's debt \Nbesides what we've been working to pay off?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also unaware of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.62,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who does this debt belong to?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.34,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Kaiser Corporation?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I think their name was something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.64,0:12:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't remember it very clearly.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.62,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably take a deeper look into this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane, let me help, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.62,0:12:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too. I'll help however I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.28,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this. Seems things \Nhave gone all complicated.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.36,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. This is our problem, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.86,0:12:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But before all that, don't you dare \Nthink about retiring. You hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, you got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.52,0:12:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something under the bed. \NMind pulling it out real quick?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you {\i1}could{\i0} say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.78,0:12:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, y'see, Shiroko came \Nand dropped it off earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.30,0:13:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it was lying \Nin front of the restaurant's ruins.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.26,0:13:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So obviously I got curious and opened it up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.32,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And wouldn't you know, it's stuffed full of cash!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This has gotta be bad news, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's from a well-meaning stranger!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.66,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I think it's perfectly fine to \Nuse this money to rebuild your restaurant!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.88,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm sure whoever left this money \Nwas inspired to do so by your ramen!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true, then I can't describe how happy that makes me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.80,0:13:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want in life is to have my hungry customers \Neat their fill on delicious ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been everything keeping me going!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting to eat your ramen again.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.82,0:13:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get better, and then rebuild your store!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.12,0:13:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And once that happens, \Nyou'd better hire me again, boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.80,0:13:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment I'm back on my feet, \NI'll feed you all the ramen you like!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.42,0:14:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather's nice. \NOut for a nap on the roof today?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.84,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of taking a little break myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.88,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been here for a good while now, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.70,0:14:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Now that I think about, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.48,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta admit, I thought you \Nwere just some weirdo at first.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.84,0:14:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been quite reliable, haven't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.68,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. You're all over the place, \Nand you're always one step behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.82,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the Task Force seems \Nhappier than they did before.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.16,0:14:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not me. Everyone's just moving \Ntowards a clear goal for the future now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you could be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika's not always trying to \Ndo things on her own anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.14,0:14:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane's not looking down as much, I guess?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.40,0:15:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi's been laughing for her own sake \Ninstead of someone else's.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Shiroko...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's breathing easier now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing your best, too. \NEveryone trusts you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.38,0:15:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This old man just wants to make sure \Nthe kids can keep being kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what leads to their happiness in the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I have to continue forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.22,0:15:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I feel a lot better after hearing you say that. \NNow I can really enjoy my nap!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.74,0:15:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought you were \Nfinally being serious for once. 
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Arona.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where did my strawberry cake go?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And my banana cake?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.12,0:16:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this my punishment for trying to eat two at once?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Arona? \NJust one bite would have been enough...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to bring some cake next time. \NStrawberry and banana, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you had to see that...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank you for the offer! \NI look forward to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what brings you here today?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.58,0:16:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, there was something I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you look into Kaiser Corporation?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Corporation?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.24,0:16:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're up to something \Nin the Abydos desert.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.54,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you'd like me \Nto look into in the meantime?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something I need to do on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm their teacher, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.48,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You're always a big help.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.80,0:17:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I am both the talented systems \Nadministrator of the Shittim Chest and its main OS.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.88,0:17:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all, I'm your helpful personal assistant!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I wonder if everyone's back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.02,0:17:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, everyone. \NHow was the boss doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.42,0:17:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He was doing great, in both health and in spirits!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He was talking about how he'll \Nrebuild Shiba Seki Ramen soon, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.14,0:17:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We've actually run into another problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We were about to talk about it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.94,0:17:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put, it seems that Abydos High School \Ndoes not own the rights to this area.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.46,0:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Doesn't the land within a \Nschool district belong to the school?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.26,0:18:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the boss, even the building that Shiba Seki Ramen was in
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't belong to Abydos High School anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.30,0:18:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know for sure, but \Nthe boss said it was a few years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.26,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who owns it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Corporation.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't start just recently.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This had been going on since before we ever met \NProblem Solver 68 or the Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.58,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been dancing to the tune of \NKaiser Corporation all along.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,God, now I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.22,0:18:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, we won't know \Nfor sure until the results come out.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that isn't the case.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.30,0:18:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like I can never get enough sleep \Nno matter how many naps I take these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just getting old.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.50,0:18:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, take a look at that! \NDoesn't that cloud look kinda like a whale?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's right there! The big one!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see it from all the way over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.80,0:19:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer. I promise I won't bite.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.02,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't push me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.20,0:19:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're in the middle of a serious \Nconversation here! This isn't the time for -
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.02,0:19:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, why don't we take a look, too, Serika?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, Nonomi? \NWhat's going on with everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.00,0:19:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that cloud right there? \NI'd say it looks more like a dolphin than a whale.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.44,0:19:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.32,0:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Hoshino means the cloud \Nabove that one, right, Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.46,0:19:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When you put it that way, \Nthe one under it does kind of look like a dolphin.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.86,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that makes the one \Nunderneath that one a jellyfish?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.78,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember jellyfish \Nlooking quite like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be some kinds that do look like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.66,0:19:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that we're on the topic, \Nlet's all go to an aquarium together!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.10,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know anything for now, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.70,0:19:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting around with a frown on our faces \Nwon't change the outcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.42,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So in that case, \NI want to at least be smiling while we wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.38,0:20:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, Serika, there's \Ntons of jellyfish over at the aquarium.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so nice to look at, all wiggly and squiggly!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, won't you indulge this old man? {timing is wonky here}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.84,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine, I'll go. Happy?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.14,0:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this might be exactly \Nwhat we need once in a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! It's important to take breaks, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming too, right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "what"? \NYou're not coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.82,0:20:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we need a teacher to chaperone us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.88,0:20:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. Sure, let's all go together!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{=3}This is gonna be so fun!

